@link http://code.google.com/p/php-mysql-master-slave-replication-monitor/wiki/InstallationAndStandardUseCase

==quick install==
download package
unzip to a web accessible folder
(optionally htaccess password protect the directory)
import the "create.util_replicaiton.sql" file
	mysql -uroot -p -h DBMASTERHOST < create.util_replicaiton.sql

